In the heart of San Francisco, the renowned Tartine Bakery bustles with activity. The aroma of fresh-baked bread fills the air. Customers, represented by a diverse mix of LEGO characters, are packed inside the small bakery, their faces lit with excitement. The bakery display is stacked high with a variety of breads, pastries, and other baked goods. A line of customers extends out the door and around the block, a testament to the bakery's popularity. The bakery staff hurries to fulfill orders, their faces flushed from the heat of the ovens.

nodeData.name: Identity Inner
nodeData.subtitle: Instinct
nodeData.shedding: Recognize compromise as your nature. Incorporating others, balancing opposites and respecting duality is appreciated. However, this measured approach must be released from the focus of your life.
nodeData.integrating: Address precarious, stagnant energy. In seeking approval, you sacrifice trust in your own instincts. Integrate your complementary desire to find ease in individuality.
nodeData.grounding: Honor your impulses. Embrace unwavering selfhood. Go on solo adventures. Grounding this energy means developing a 'me' focus, taking risks with confidence.

nodeData.name: Experience Inner
nodeData.subtitle: Seen
nodeData.shedding: Recognize intensity as your nature. Transformation, energy contracts, emotional complexity are appreciated. However, this deep, entangled approach must be released from the focus of your life.
nodeData.integrating: Address mistrusting, chaos-prone energy. Involving in power dynamics, protecting against the shadow side of situations, you sacrifice ease and calm. Integrate your complementary desire for stable self-reliance.
nodeData.grounding: Center your value. Settle into structure. Be in nature. Please your senses. Form boundaries to preserve your peace. Draw power from serenity and reliable experiences.

nodeData.name: Language Inner
nodeData.subtitle: Ideas
nodeData.shedding: Recognize philosophy and adventure as your nature. Seeing the bigger picture is appreciated. However, this profound approach must be released from the focus of your life.
nodeData.integrating: Address unapproachable energy. Exalting your virtues or exaggerated personal freedom comes at the sacrifice of simple curiosity. Integrate a complementary desire to converse without bias.
nodeData.grounding: Let others inform you. Play with ideas. Detach from staunch perspectives. Grounding this energy means embracing the temporary nature of a zeitgeist.

nodeData.name: Domain Inner
nodeData.subtitle: Source
nodeData.shedding: Recognize material ambition as your nature. Climbing to reach tangible goals is appreciated. However, this stoic approach must be released from the focus of your life.
nodeData.integrating: Address melancholic energy. Pursuing established status for yourself or others, you sacrifice nurturing internal emotions and external connections. Integrate a complementary need for vulnerability, deep personal experiences.
nodeData.grounding: Tend to your feelings. Create rituals. Withdraw from public eyes. Nurture the hearts of others, helping you pour into yourself.

nodeData.name: Purpose Inner
nodeData.subtitle: Heart
nodeData.shedding: Recognize logic as your nature. Progressive, humanitarian thinking is appreciated. However, this intellectual approach must be released from the focus of your life.
nodeData.integrating: Address detached, group-oriented energy. Focusing on collective needs or social advocacy, you sacrifice the inner child desire for play. Integrate your complementary desire for creative expression.
nodeData.grounding: Lead with your heart. Integrate drama. Initiate romance. Take center stage and inspire others. Love and generosity will help you channel your innate altruism into purposeful achievements.

nodeData.name: Order Inner
nodeData.subtitle: Parts
nodeData.shedding: Recognize sensitivity as your nature. Being connected and visionary with keen intuition is appreciated. However, this fluid approach must be released from the focus of your life.
nodeData.integrating: Address self-undoing energy. Empathizing with those around you, you sacrifice your emotional health and psychic wellbeing. Integrate a complementary desire to say no.
nodeData.grounding: Create healthy structure and routine. Get organized. Maintain physical and energetic tidiness. Make detail-oriented plans.

nodeData.name: Identity Outer
nodeData.subtitle: Reason
nodeData.shedding: Recognize individuating as your nature. Drive, discovery and following your instincts is appreciated. However, this youthful just-do-it approach must be released from the focus of your life.
nodeData.integrating: Address impulsive, self-focused energy. Blazing your path, you sacrifice the ability to integrate complementary people or perspectives. Integrate your desire to experience ease in partnership.
nodeData.grounding: Share, hold space for others. Consider their needs and experience. See both sides of an argument before making decisions.

nodeData.name: Experience Outer
nodeData.subtitle: Unseen
nodeData.shedding: Recognize sensuality and stability as your nature. Steadfastness is appreciated. However this slow, steady approach must be released from the focus of your life.
nodeData.integrating: Address controlling, rigid energy. Holding on to situations or a comfort zone, you sacrifice deep personal growth opportunities. Integrate a complementary desire to purge, exchange and experience transformation.
nodeData.grounding: Go deep and transmute. Discard stale limitations. Release unnecessary boundaries. The more you let go, the more you step into new life.

nodeData.name: Language Outer
nodeData.subtitle: Ideology
nodeData.shedding: Recognize intellectual adaptability as your nature. Assimilating social codes and information is appreciated. However, this impartial approach must be released from the focus of your life.
nodeData.integrating: Address duplicitous energy. Tailoring your speech to an audience or environment, you sacrifice expressing your truth. Integrate a complementary desire to be honest, see the forest for the trees.
nodeData.grounding: Unplug from external perspectives. Anchor your beliefs, speak confidently from that place. Cultivate faith that lights the way from within.

nodeData.name: Domain Outer
nodeData.subtitle: Resource
nodeData.shedding: Recognize tenderness as your nature. Nurturing your feelings, being cautious is appreciated. However, this sensitive approach must be released from the focus of your life.
nodeData.integrating: Address needy or wary emotional energy. Staying rooted, keeping things close, you sacrifice stepping into greater responsibility to realize substantive foundations. Integrate your complementary need to manage practical affairs.
nodeData.grounding: Shoulder important endeavors. Be pragmatic. Take charge with integrity. Consider your legacy in the world, maintaining healthy long-term goals.

nodeData.name: Purpose Outer
nodeData.subtitle: Head
nodeData.shedding: Recognize leadership or artistry as your nature. Commanding the center of attention is appreciated. However, passion and showiness must be released from the focus of your life.
nodeData.integrating: Address bossy, attention-seeking energy. Displaying talents for praise or pleasure, you sacrifice contributing to group advancements. Integrate a complementary desire to consider collective efforts.
nodeData.grounding: Advocate for social cause. Be future-minded. Explore your innovative, intellectual side. Join a group or network.

nodeData.name: Order Outer
nodeData.subtitle: Whole
nodeData.shedding: Recognize precision as your nature. Attention to detail and methodical plans are appreciated. However, this meticulous approach must be released from the focus of your life.
nodeData.integrating: Address critical, perfectionistic energy. Analyzing presentation and results, you sacrifice gentleness with yourself and others. Integrate a complementary desire to release and forgive.
nodeData.grounding: Go with the flow. Develop a spiritual practice. Tune out physical concerns. Listen to intuition.
